overview: It's not very often a lady like Chessie Moore decides to bare it all for the camera. And even rarer for such a special lady to go all the way. But all the way she goes -i and we mean back way too, in "New Girl in Town." Also, featuring the stunning Racquel Darrian, the beautiful Tamara Lee, and the foxxy Renee Foxx. Don't miss "New Girl," after all, 44EE's aren't flying in on every bus!
title: New Girl In Town
